PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of RANDOLPH WILLIAM DROVER of Bishop's Falls, Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Marine Atlantic Inc., to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of John Brent Chaffey, whose term has expired.
